title: Divine Hero’s Skyfall System
alternative_titles: Shen Hao's Heavenly Fall System 神豪之天降系统
summary: Divine Hero’s Skyfall System [All Chapter] English Translation After three years of being a son-in-law, Xiao Ge was subjected to countless stares and insults. However, his wife’s kindness and beauty made it difficult for him to let go. Finally, he awakens the Divine Hero System, and begins a life of pushy and unpredictable behavior.
